HEADWORD: Lightroom
<hw>Light"room`</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧t"r⟦oomac⟧m`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A small room from which the magazine of a naval vessel is lighted,
being separated from the magazine by heavy glass windows.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

